metadata.name: RocketMan #1
metadata.description: Rocket Man is a proud collection of 8000 avatars celebrating your stance on positivity, self-affirmation, dignity, equal rights and visibility as a social group. It represents the chance to be true to yourself with others in the community. Rocket Man holders will receive exclusive access to future drops, social events and much more. Visit https://RocketMan.wtf for details and all upcoming plans.
